      "content": "OGC Streaming services exposing Maxar's current and historical imagery as WMS, WMTS and WFS layers — implemented behind securewatch.maxar.com and surfaced through the MGP_SDK Python, Java and R clients. Profile derived from the MGP_SDK README (\"Open Geospatial Consortium standard protocols: WFS, WMS, WMTS\"); endpoint paths follow standard OGC URL patterns.",
